from datetime import datetime

# Define the departure and arrival times
departure_time = datetime.strptime("03:19:59", "%H:%M:%S")
arrival_time = datetime.strptime("12:42:10", "%H:%M:%S")

# Calculate the duration of the flight
flight_duration = arrival_time - departure_time

# Format the duration in HH:MM:SS
flight_duration_str = str(flight_duration)

flight_duration_str
